~~ flask guide ~~

install with pip

export the mode (auto-reload and debug) and app:
$ export FLASK_APP=hello.py
$ export FLASK_ENV=development

and start the server with
$ flask run

a minimalistic hello.py is in
  repos/aavo/www/mflask.py

-- host=0.0.0.0 to make it available to the network

Jinja: http://jinja.pocoo.org/docs/2.10/templates/

